<h2>Two-Factor Authentication</h2>

<p>Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>

<p>
  Your two-factor authentication code for ProFile AI is below. Enter this
  code on the sign-in screen to continue.
</p>

<div class="otp-box">
  <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
  <div class="otp-timer">⏱ This code expires in <%= expiryMinutes %> minutes</div>
</div>

<p class="muted">
  If you did not attempt to sign in, please change your password immediately
  and review your active sessions from <strong>Profile → Devices</strong>.
</p>